
# Schema for `/project`

**Resolved from:**

- `/project/.ta/schema.toml`


docs

    shape   collection
    path    docs
    format  md

  Long-form documentation set.


docs.note

    heading  1

  One markdown note per file.

  body
    type      string
    required  yes
    format    markdown

  The document body. Whole-file content goes here.


plans

    shape   file
    path    plans.toml
    format  toml

  Project planning db.


plans.task

  A unit of work in the plan.

  id
    type      string
    required  yes

  Stable identifier for the task. Matches the file-atom prefix so `ta get plans.task.t1` locates this record independent of heading edits.

  priority
    type      integer
    required  no
    default   3

  Lower numbers sort earlier. Callers may omit; default is 3 (normal).

  status
    type      string
    required  yes
    default   todo
    enum      [todo, doing, done, blocked]

  Lifecycle state of the task.
